injectables.name: AppEffects

properties.name: initCategorias$
properties.defaultValue:
createEffect(() =>
        this.actions.pipe(
            ofType(InitApp),
            switchMap(() => this.service.ObtenerCategorias()),
            filter(categorias => !!categorias),
            map(categorias => categoriesObtained({categorias}))
            ))

components.name: AppComponent
components.templateData:
<header>
	@if (mainToolbar$ | async; as mainToolbar) {
		<toolbar-feature [toolbar]="mainToolbar" />
	}
	@if (isMenuOpened$ | async) {
		@if (secondaryToolbar$ | async; as secondaryToolbar) {
			<toolbar-feature [toolbar]="secondaryToolbar" />
		}
	}
</header>
<main>
	<mat-drawer-container (backdropClick)="onBackdropClicked()">
		<mat-drawer
			mode="over"
			[opened]="isShoppingCartOpened$ | async"
			position="end"
		>
			<shopping-cart-ui />
		</mat-drawer>
		<mat-drawer-content>
			<list-feature
				[id]="'app-list'"
				[titulo]="listTitle$"
				[data$]="data$"
			/>
		</mat-drawer-content>
	</mat-drawer-container>
</main>
